üéØ Comprehensive research to design a new Terraform-only edge component that integrates Azure Machine Learning with Arc-enabled Kubernetes. The component must mirror the cloud component structure, store AzureML SSL material as Key Vault secrets (in the edge component), and rely on Kubernetes resources (namespace, SecretProviderClass, SecretSync) applied by the IoT Operations edge component.

